title: 324. Andy & DJ CTI: Biden's Voicemail To Hunter, Hutchinson's Jan 6th Testimony & Serious Adverse Events
itunes:title: 324. Andy & DJ CTI: Biden's Voicemail To Hunter, Hutchinson's Jan 6th Testimony & Serious Adverse Events
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss the leaked voicemail message from President Biden to Hunter regarding his dealings with the Chinese, Cassidy Hutchinson's testimony describing Donald Trump's actions on January 6th, and the serious adverse events that have occurred due to the Covid-19 vaccine.
